  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Superior Rooms </strong>have a balcony and sea views. They are spacious and located on the upper floors of the hotel, looking out across the gardens and the Amalfi Coast. They're decorated with handcrafted terracotta, Vietri ceramic tiled floors and antique wooden furniture. Facilities include a furnished balcony, air conditioning, TV, minibar, hairdryer and shower or whirlpool bath.</p>
<p><strong>Standard Rooms</strong> are about 18m² and have sea views from the furnished private balcony. These rooms are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Family Rooms </strong>are locates on the lower floor of the hotel with views of the seafront and terraces. They have a lounge study area attached to the bedroom with a two-seater sofa that can be used as a sofa bed and a private balcony with chairs and a coffee table. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
